{"kanda":6,"sarga":117,"description":"","verses":[{"v":1,"dev":"स उवाचमहाप्रामस्सोऽभिवाद्यप्लवङ्गमः ।रामंवचनमर्थज्ञोवरंसर्वधनुष्मताम्","trans":"Highly learned Hanuman greeted and spoke meaningfully to Rama, the foremost among the wielders of bow.","words":[{"d":"महाप्राज्ञः","m":"highly learned"},{"d":"सःप्लवङ्गमः","m":"that monkey"},{"d":"वचनमर्थज्ञो","m":"meaningful"},{"d":"सर्वधनुष्मताम्","m":"foremost among the wielders of bow"},{"d":"वरम्","m":"choicest"},{"d":"तंरामम्","m":"Rama"},{"d":"अभिवाद्य","m":"greeted"},{"d":"उवाच","m":"spoke"}]},{"v":2,"dev":"यन्निमित्तोऽयमारम्बःकर्मणांयःफलोदयः ।तांदेवींशोकसन्तप्तांद्रष्टुमर्हसिमैथिलीम्","trans":"\"You ought to see that noble lady Mythili, who was immersed in grief, for whose sake these actions were started and has borne fruit.\"","words":[{"d":"कर्मणाम्","m":"these actions"},{"d":"अयम्","m":"this"},{"d":"आरम्बः","m":"started"},{"d":"यन्निमित्तः","m":"for whose sake"},{"d":"यः","m":"he who"},{"d":"फलोदयः","m":"has borne fruit"},{"d":"ताम्","m":"her"},{"d":"शोकसन्तप्ताम्","m":"immersed in grief"},{"d":"देवीम्","m":"noble lady"},{"d":"मैथिलीम्","m":"Mythili"},{"d":"द्रष्टुम्","m":"to see"},{"d":"अर्हसि","m":"ought to"}]},{"v":3,"dev":"साहिशोकसमाविष्टाबाष्पपर्याकुलेक्षणा ।मैथिलीविजयंश्रुत्वाद्रष्टुंत्वामभिकाङ्क्षति","trans":"\"Mythili who is overcome with grief on hearing your victory, was filled with tears in her eyes and desired to see you.\"","words":[{"d":"शोकसमाविष्टाः","m":"who is overcome with grief"},{"d":"सामैथिली","m":"she, Mythili"},{"d":"विजयम्","m":"victory"},{"d":"श्रुत्वा","m":"hearing"},{"d":"बाष्पपर्याकुलेक्षणा","m":"eyes filled with tears"},{"d":"त्वाम्","m":"you"},{"d":"द्रष्टुम्","m":"to see"},{"d":"अभिकाङ्क्षति","m":"desired"}]},{"v":4,"dev":"पूर्वकात्प्रत्ययाच्चाहमुक्तोविश्वस्तयातया ।भर्तारंद्रष्टुमिच्छामिकृतार्थंसहलक्ष्मणम्","trans":"\"In an earlier occasion having known me and trusting me expressed that she desires to see Rama with Lakshmana after victory and with gratitude.\"","words":[{"d":"पूर्वकात्","m":"earlier occasion"},{"d":"प्रत्ययात्","m":"expressed"},{"d":"विश्वस्तया","m":"trust"},{"d":"तया","m":"so also"},{"d":"अहम्","m":"I"},{"d":"उक्तः","m":"said"},{"d":"कृतार्थम्","m":"gratitude"},{"d":"सहलक्ष्मणम्","m":"with Lakshmana"},{"d":"भर्तारम्","m":"husband"},{"d":"द्रष्टुम्","m":"to see"},{"d":"इच्छामि","m":"desire"}]},{"v":5,"dev":"एवमुक्तोहनुमतारामोधर्मभृतांवरः ।आगच्छत्सहसाध्यानमीषद्भाष्पपरिप्लुतः","trans":"When Hanuman had spoken like that, Rama, the upholder of righteousness, shed tears slightly and suddenly became thoughtful.","words":[{"d":"हनुमता","m":"Hanuman"},{"d":"एवम्","m":"in that way"},{"d":"उक्तः","m":"having spoken"},{"d":"धर्मभृताम्","m":"upholder of righteousness"},{"d":"वरः","m":"best"},{"d":"रामः","m":"Rama"},{"d":"ईषत्","m":"slightly"},{"d":"बाष्पपरिप्लुतः","m":"shed tears from eyes"},{"d":"सहसा","m":"suddenly"},{"d":"ध्यानम्","m":"thoughtful"},{"d":"आगच्छत्","m":"became"}]},{"v":6,"dev":"दीर्घमुष्णंविनिःश्वस्यजगतीमवलोकयन् ।उवाचमेघसङ्काशंविभीषणमुपस्थितम्","trans":"Drawing a long hot breath, looking at the ground, he spoke to Vibheeshana, who was like a cloud standing there.","words":[{"d":"दीर्घम्","m":"long"},{"d":"उष्णम्","m":"hot"},{"d":"विनिःश्वस्य","m":"drawing breath"},{"d":"जगतीम्","m":"on the world"},{"d":"अवलोकयन्","m":"looking at"},{"d":"उपस्थितम्","m":"standing"},{"d":"मेघसङ्काशम्","m":"resembling a cloud in colour"},{"d":"विभीषणम्","m":"Vibheeshana"},{"d":"उवाच","m":"spoke"}]},{"v":7,"dev":"दिव्याङ्गरागांवैदेहींदिव्याभरणभूषिताम् ।इहसीतांशिरःस्नातामुपस्थापयमाचिरम्","trans":"","words":[{"d":"शिरःस्नाताम्","m":"after head bath"},{"d":"दिव्याङ्गरागाम्","m":"anointed with fragrance"},{"d":"दिव्यायभरणभूषिताम्","m":"decorated with wonderful ornaments"},{"d":"सीताम्","m":"Sita"},{"d":"इह","m":"here"},{"d":"उपस्थापय","m":"bring"},{"d":"चिरम्","m":"quickly"},{"d":"मा","m":"bring"}]},{"v":8,"dev":"एवमुक्तस्तुरामेणत्वरमाणोविभीषणः ।प्रविश्यान्तःपुरंसीतांस्त्रीभिस्स्वाभिरोचदयत्","trans":"When Rama had spoken in that manner, Vibheeeshana for his part hastened to the Gynaeceum and assigned through the women to convey to Sita.","words":[{"d":"एवम्","m":"in that manner"},{"d":"रामेण","m":"by Rama"},{"d":"उक्तः","m":"spoken"},{"d":"विभीषणः","m":"Vibheeshana"},{"d":"त्वरमाणः","m":"hastened"},{"d":"अन्तःपुरम्","m":"to the gynaeceum"},{"d":"प्रविश्य","m":"entered"},{"d":"स्वाभिः","m":"for his part"},{"d":"स्त्रीभिः","m":"women"},{"d":"सीताम्","m":"to Sita"},{"d":"अचोदयात्","m":"conveyed"}]},{"v":9,"dev":"ततस्सीतांमहाभागांदृष्टवोवाचविभीषणः ।मूर्ध्निबद्धाञ्जलिश्रीमान्विनीतोराक्षसेश्वरः","trans":"Then Vibheeshana, the prosperous Lord of the Rakshasas seeing Sita greeted her with palms joined together lifted it over his head (as a sign of respect).","words":[{"d":"ततः","m":"then"},{"d":"श्रीमान्","m":"prosperous"},{"d":"विभीषणः","m":"Vibheeshana"},{"d":"महाभागाम्","m":"the noble"},{"d":"सीताम्","m":"to Sita"},{"d":"दृष्टवा","m":"seeing"},{"d":"विनीतः","m":"his head"},{"d":"मूर्ध्निः","m":"head"},{"d":"बद्धाञ्जलिः","m":"with palms joined"},{"d":"उवाच","m":"spoke"}]},{"v":10,"dev":"दिव्याङ्गरागावैदेहीदिव्याभरणभूषिता ।यानमारोहभद्रंतेभर्तात्वांद्रष्टुमिच्छति","trans":"\"Vaidehi! Anointed with a wonderful fragrance, decked with beautiful ornaments, auspicious and ascending the palanquin, your husband desires to see you.\"","words":[{"d":"वैदेही","m":"Vaidehi"},{"d":"दिव्याङ्गरागा","m":"anointed with wonderful fragrance"},{"d":"दिव्याभरणभूषिता","m":"decked with beautiful ornaments"},{"d":"यानम्","m":"palanquin"},{"d":"आरोह","m":"ascending"},{"d":"ते","m":"you"},{"d":"भद्रम्","m":"auspicious"},{"d":"भर्ता","m":"husband"},{"d":"त्वाम्","m":"you"},{"d":"द्रष्टुम्","m":"to see"},{"d":"इच्छति","m":"desires"}]},{"v":11,"dev":"एवमुक्तातुवैदेहीप्रत्युवाचविभीषणम् ।अस्नात्वाद्रष्टुमिच्छामिभर्तारंराक्षसेश्वर","trans":"Vibheeshana, having spoken that way, Vaidehi said to the Lord of Rakshasas that she would like to see him without having a bath.","words":[{"d":"एवम्","m":"in that way"},{"d":"उक्ता","m":"spoken"},{"d":"वैदेही","m":"Vaidehi"},{"d":"विभीषणम्","m":"to Vibheeshana"},{"d":"प्रत्युवाच","m":"replied"},{"d":"राक्षसेश्वर","m":"Lord of Rakshasas"},{"d":"अस्नात्वा","m":"without bath"},{"d":"भर्तारम्","m":"husband"},{"d":"द्रष्टुम्","m":"see"},{"d":"इच्छामि","m":"I desire"}]},{"v":12,"dev":"तस्यास्तद्वचनंश्रुत्वाप्रत्युवाचविभीषणः ।यथाहरामोभहर्तातेतत्तथाकर्तुमार्हसिमार्हसि","trans":"Hearing Sita's words Vibheeshana replied saying,\" You will and ought to do what your husband Rama has said.\"","words":[{"d":"तस्याः","m":"her"},{"d":"तत्","m":"that"},{"d":"वचनम्","m":"words"},{"d":"श्रुत्वा","m":"hearing"},{"d":"प्रत्युवाच","m":"replied in turn"},{"d":"ते","m":"you"},{"d":"भर्ता","m":"husband"},{"d":"यथा","m":"so"},{"d":"आह","m":"I"},{"d":"तत्","m":"that"},{"d":"तथआ","m":"that only"},{"d":"कर्तुम्","m":"will do"},{"d":"अर्हसि","m":"ought to"}]},{"v":13,"dev":"तस्यतद्वचनंश्रुत्वामैथिलीपतिदेवता ।भर्तृभक्त्यावृतासाध्वीतथेतिप्रत्यभाषत","trans":"Noble Mythili (on hearing Vibheeshana), who looked upon her husband as God, said in reply, 'Alright'.","words":[{"d":"पतिदेवता","m":"husband as god"},{"d":"साध्वी","m":"noble"},{"d":"मैथिली","m":"Mythili"},{"d":"तस्य","m":"her"},{"d":"तत्","m":"that"},{"d":"वचनम्","m":"words"},{"d":"श्रुत्वा","m":"hearing"},{"d":"भर्तृभक्त्या","m":"in devotion"},{"d":"वृता","m":"adorned"},{"d":"तथेति","m":"alright"},{"d":"प्रत्यभाषत","m":"replied in turn"}]},{"v":14,"dev":"ततस्सीतांशिरःस्नातांसंयुक्तांप्रतिकर्मणा ।महार्हाभरणोपेतांमहार्हाम्बरधारिणीम् आरोप्यशिबिकांदीप्तांपरार्घ्याम्बरसम्वृताम् ।राक्षसैर्भहुभिर्गुप्तामाजहारविभीषणः","trans":"Thereafter Vibheeshana, making Sita to ascend the palanquin, covered with valuable clothes and guarded by numerous Rakshasas after she adorned herself in the best of ornaments and put on glowing wonderful clothes brought to Rama.","words":[{"d":"ततः","m":"thereafter"},{"d":"विभीषणः","m":"Vibheeshana"},{"d":"शिरःस्नाताम्","m":"head bath"},{"d":"प्रतिकर्मणा","m":"personal decoration"},{"d":"संयुक्ताम्","m":"together"},{"d":"महार्हाभरणोपेताम्","m":"best of ornaments"},{"d":"महार्हाम्बरधारिणीम्","m":"wonderful clothes"},{"d":"सीताम्","m":"Sita"},{"d":"दीप्ताम्","m":"glowing"},{"d":"परार्घ्याम्बरसंवृताम्","m":"covered with wonderful clothes"},{"d":"बहुभिः","m":"numerous"},{"d":"राक्षसैः","m":"Rakshasas"},{"d":"गुप्ताम्","m":"guarded by"},{"d":"शिबिकाम्","m":"palanquin"},{"d":"आरोप्य","m":"ascended"},{"d":"आजहार","m":"brought"}]},{"v":15,"dev":"ततस्सीतांशिरःस्नातांसंयुक्तांप्रतिकर्मणा ।महार्हाभरणोपेतांमहार्हाम्बरधारिणीम् आरोप्यशिबिकांदीप्तांपरार्घ्याम्बरसम्वृताम् ।राक्षसैर्भहुभिर्गुप्तामाजहारविभीषणः","trans":"Thereafter Vibheeshana, making Sita to ascend the palanquin, covered with valuable clothes and guarded by numerous Rakshasas after she adorned herself in the best of ornaments and put on glowing wonderful clothes brought to Rama.","words":[{"d":"ततः","m":"thereafter"},{"d":"विभीषणः","m":"Vibheeshana"},{"d":"शिरःस्नाताम्","m":"head bath"},{"d":"प्रतिकर्मणा","m":"personal decoration"},{"d":"संयुक्ताम्","m":"together"},{"d":"महार्हाभरणोपेताम्","m":"best of ornaments"},{"d":"महार्हाम्बरधारिणीम्","m":"wonderful clothes"},{"d":"सीताम्","m":"Sita"},{"d":"दीप्ताम्","m":"glowing"},{"d":"परार्घ्याम्बरसंवृताम्","m":"covered with wonderful clothes"},{"d":"बहुभिः","m":"numerous"},{"d":"राक्षसैः","m":"Rakshasas"},{"d":"गुप्ताम्","m":"guarded by"},{"d":"शिबिकाम्","m":"palanquin"},{"d":"आरोप्य","m":"ascended"},{"d":"आजहार","m":"brought"}]},{"v":16,"dev":"सोऽभिगम्यमहात्मानंज्ञातावपिध्यानमास्थितम् ।प्रणतश्चप्रहृष्टश्चप्राप्तांसीतांन्यवेदयत्","trans":"Knowing that Sita reached also, great Rama was seen in a meditative mood absorbed in thought. Vibheeshana announced saying, 'Sita has been brought' and greeted with folded palms, full of joy.","words":[{"d":"सः","m":"he"},{"d":"ज्ञात्वापि","m":"after knowing"},{"d":"द्यानम्","m":"meditative mood"},{"d":"आस्थितम्","m":"absorbed in thought"},{"d":"महात्मानम्","m":"great"},{"d":"अभिगम्य","m":"having reached"},{"d":"प्रणतः च","m":"greeting with folded palms"},{"d":"प्रहृष्टश्च","m":"full of joy"},{"d":"सीताम्","m":"Sita"},{"d":"प्राप्ताम्","m":"arrived"},{"d":"न्यवेदयत्","m":"announced"}]},{"v":17,"dev":"तामागतामुपश्रुत्यरक्षोगृहचिरोषिताम् ।हर्षोदैन्यंच रोषश्चत्रयंराघवमाविशत्","trans":"On hearing that Sita had arrived, who stayed in Rakshasa's abode for long, Raghava had experienced joy, indignation, and anger, all the three at the same time.","words":[{"d":"रक्षोगृहचिरोषिताम्","m":"stayed in Rakshasa's abode for long"},{"d":"ताम्","m":"her"},{"d":"आगताम्","m":"reached"},{"d":"उपश्रुत्य","m":"having heard"},{"d":"राघवम्","m":"Raghava"},{"d":"हर्षः","m":"joyful"},{"d":"दैन्यम्","m":"indignation"},{"d":"रोषश्च","m":"anger"},{"d":"त्रयम्","m":"three"},{"d":"आविशत्","m":"experienced"}]},{"v":18,"dev":"ततःपार्श्वगतंदृष्टवासविमर्शंविचारयन् ।विभीषणमिदंवाक्यमहृष्टोराघवोऽब्रवीत्","trans":"Raghava, analysed with in him, distressed and thinking deeply, seeing Vibheeshana close by, spoke these words.","words":[{"d":"ततः","m":"then"},{"d":"सविमर्शम्","m":"analysing with in"},{"d":"विचारयन्","m":"thinking"},{"d":"पार्श्वगतम्","m":"who had come near"},{"d":"विभीषणम्","m":"Vibheeshana"},{"d":"इदम्","m":"these"},{"d":"अब्रवीत्","m":"spoke"}]},{"v":19,"dev":"राक्षसाधिपतेसौम्यनित्यंमद्विजयेरत ।वैदेहीसंनिकर्षंमेशीघ्रंसमुपगच्छतु","trans":"\"O gentle Vibheeshana, let Sita who sought my victory always be quickly brought near me.\"","words":[{"d":"नित्यम्","m":"always"},{"d":"मद्विजये","m":"my victory"},{"d":"रत","m":"sought"},{"d":"सौम्य","m":"gentle"},{"d":"राक्षसाधिपते","m":"Rakshasa king"},{"d":"शीघ्रम्","m":"quickly"},{"d":"मे","m":"my"},{"d":"सन्निकर्षम्","m":"near"},{"d":"समुपगच्छतु","m":"let her be brought"}]},{"v":20,"dev":"तस्यतद्वचनंश्रुत्वाराघवस्यविभीषणः ।तूर्णमुत्सारणंतत्रकारयामासधर्मवित्","trans":"On hearing Raghava's words, faithful Vibheeshana instantly assigned people to disperse from there.","words":[{"d":"तस्यराघवस्य","m":"Raghava's"},{"d":"तत्","m":"that"},{"d":"वचनम्","m":"words"},{"d":"श्रुत्वा","m":"on hearing"},{"d":"धर्मवित्"